high_descs: Head toward to the fridge then turn right to reach countertop.
Pick the banana from the table.
Turn left to reach the microwave.
Put the banana into the microwave.
After take the banana from the sink
Put the banana on the top of the sink.

high_descs: Head rotate and turn right to the countertop.
Turn right to the banana and turn left to the microwave oven.
Pick the banana from the microwave.
Place the banana inside the microwave oven.
Pick it back from the sink.
Turn back and place the banana on the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the banana on the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and then right to walk out of the room, turn left and enter into kitchen and stand in front of the countertop.
Pick up the banana lying near the oven.
Turn left and then right to stand in front of the microwave.
Place the banana in the oven and keep the banana there for some time and take the banana out.
Turn around and stand against the kitchen sink.
Place the banana near the sink.
anns.task_desc: Find the banana, heat it in the oven and place it near the sink.
